{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T04:23:02.189Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Deep Learning (DL)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is a specialized subset of machine learning that uses artificial neural networks with many layers to learn complex patterns from data, especially unstructured data like images, speech, and text."}]}, {"type": "blockquote", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key idea:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " DL is “machine learning with deep neural networks” — the “deep” refers to the many layers in the network."}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Deep Learning — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "DL in the hierarchy: AI → ML → DL → Gen AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Deep Learning sits inside ML, which is inside AI:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "AI (Artificial Intelligence)\n └── ML (Machine Learning)\n      └── DL (Deep Learning)\n           └── Gen AI (Generative AI, often built on DL models)"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Any system that mimics human intelligence (rules, search, planning, ML, etc.)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": AI that learns patterns from data using statistical algorithms"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "DL"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": ML that uses "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "deep neural networks"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with multiple layers to learn hierarchical representations"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Gen AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": AI that creates new content (text, images, code), typically using deep learning models like transformers"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How Deep Learning works: neural networks and layers"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "DL is built on "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "artificial neural networks"}, {"type": "text", "text": " inspired by the human brain:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "A neural network has "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "layers of nodes (“neurons”)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " connected by weighted edges"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "“Deep”"}, {"type": "text", "text": " means many layers (often 10s to 100s+) that process data in a hierarchy:"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- Early layers learn simple patterns (edges, tones, basic shapes) - Middle layers learn more complex patterns (parts of objects, syllables) - Late layers learn abstract concepts (faces, words, objects)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "nested hierarchy of concepts"}, {"type": "text", "text": " allows DL to handle tasks that are extremely hard for classical ML, such as:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Face recognition (Face ID)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Self-driving car perception"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Speech recognition (“Hey Google”)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Language translation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "DL’s popularity exploded around "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "2012"}, {"type": "text", "text": " after "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "AlexNet"}, {"type": "text", "text": " dramatically won an image recognition challenge, enabled by:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Massive datasets from the internet"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Powerful GPUs (from gaming)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Improved training algorithms"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical Machine Learning vs. Deep Learning"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even within ML, there are two major approaches: "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "classical ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": " and "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "deep learning"}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical Machine Learning"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Deep Learning"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Model type"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Often simple models: linear/logistic regression, SVM, trees, random forests, k-means"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Deep neural networks (CNNs, RNNs, Transformers)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Feature handling"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Often requires "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "manual feature engineering"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (you design features)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Automatic feature learning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " from raw data (images, text, audio)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data type"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mainly "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "structured/tabular"}, {"type": "text", "text": " data"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mainly "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "unstructured"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": images, speech, text, video"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data size"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Works well with "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "smaller datasets"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Needs "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "large datasets"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to perform well"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Compute"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Runs on CPUs; low compute cost"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Requires "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "GPUs/accelerators"}, {"type": "text", "text": "; high compute cost"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Performance on complex tasks"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Struggles with very complex patterns (e.g., image/speech)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Excels at complex patterns (vision, speech, language)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Interpretability"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "More interpretable, easier to explain"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Less interpretable, “black box”"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Typical use cases"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Fraud detection, churn prediction, sales forecasting, spam filters"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Image recognition, object detection, speech recognition, NLP, translation"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental model"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Classical ML = statistician"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": finds patterns using simple models, often with hand-crafted features."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Deep Learning = visual/audio/language learner"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": learns features automatically from raw data using layered networks."}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Deep Learning as the backbone of Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generative AI is largely powered by deep learning"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Transformers"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (e.g., LLMs like ChatGPT) are deep neural networks"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "GANs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Generative Adversarial Networks) and "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Diffusion models"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (e.g., DALL·E, Midjourney) are deep learning architectures"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "VAEs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Variational Autoencoders) are also deep generative models"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "In technical terms:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical ML models often learn "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "conditional probability"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "P(\\text{output} \\mid \\text{input})"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " — e.g., “Given this image, what’s the label?”\n- Generative DL models learn the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "joint distribution"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of the data: "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "P(\\text{data})"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " — e.g., “What does language (or images) look like overall?” and then sample new examples."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "So:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "DL"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = deep neural networks that learn complex patterns"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Gen AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = deep learning models that learn the data distribution and "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "generate new content"}, {"type": "text", "text": " from it"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Deep Learning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is a specialized subset of ML using multi-layer neural networks to learn hierarchical representations from data."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Classical ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": " uses simpler models, often needs manual features, and is strong on tabular data; "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "DL"}, {"type": "text", "text": " learns features automatically and is strong on images, speech, and text."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "DL requires "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "large data + GPUs"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", while classical ML is cheaper, faster, and more interpretable."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generative AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is built on deep learning: transformers, GANs, diffusion models — all DL architectures."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "DL is the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "powerhouse"}, {"type": "text", "text": " behind Face ID, self-driving cars, speech recognition, and modern LLMs."}]}]}]}]}}